Abstract = {{We propose a model-based geostatistical approach to deal with
   regionalized compositions. We combine the additive-log-ratio
   transformation with multivariate geostatistical models whose covariance
   matrix is adapted to take into account the correlation induced by the
   compositional structure. Such specification allows the usage of standard
   likelihood methods for parameters estimation. For spatial prediction we
